source.name: Bronx Hurricane Sandy Damaged Trees
source.description: damaged tree complaints logged in three days after Hurricane Sandy. The source file is updated automatically and is logging in tree damage not associated with the storm, so I isolated the damage reports to the following three days after the storm. This dataset is historical and will not be updated.
